  <brief_title>Effectiveness of Spot-on ™ to Prevent Inadvertent Perioperative Hypothermia and Their Consecuences</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effectiveness of Spot-on ™ to Prevent Inadvertent Perioperative Hypothermia and Their Consecuences</official_title>
